Package chemaxon.struc.sgroup Description

S-group related classes and interfaces.

Serialization of the classes is `standardized' in Marvin 3.1.4. All future versions of them are planned to remain backward compatible with older versions serialized in 3.1.4 or later; the serialVersionUID's will not change.
